title: D&D 4e
description:
This is a big bunch of D&D 4e books, mainly for character creation, without adventures, but there's a bunch of stuff. Browse the torrent before starting and just select what you want if that's your jam.
There is a word document in the "Dragon Magazine" folder that has a brief synopsis of each of the issues. (eg. Specific Class/Race powers/feats and items)
I'd recommend that if you're not wanting to use the character builders then it's super useful to know where you can find possible feats and powers.
Lemme know if there's any problems with any of the files
